Metadata: University of California Sea Grant/San Diego County Cooperative Extension

Tidelines will be published quarterly as a local newsletter dealing with practical problems in the areas of Commercial and sport fisheries; Seafood processing, aquaculture, marine education and youth programs, marine research, waterfront management, boating industry, marine transportation, environmental policy, and coastal engineering. Cover articles in these issues include Tax law changes for 1985, marine mammal strandings, Fire afloat, blue water diving guidelines, Tsunami, Clean/cook/can albacore tuna, National Sea Grant Depository, Soy of the Sea (surimi).
